    <published>2016-09-01T12:37:27.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-09-01T12:55:37.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>使用return键退出键盘</strong></p>
<p>1.<em>textField</em></p>
<pre><code>使用代理  

准守协议:class ViewController: UIViewController, UITextFieldDelegate

设置代理对象:textField.delegate = self

实现代理方法:

func textFieldShouldReturn(textField: UITextField) -&gt; Bool {
    textField.resignFirstResponder()
    return true;
}
</code></pre><p>2.<em>textView</em></p>
<pre><code>使用代理

准守协议:class ViewController: UIViewController, UITextViewDelegate

设置代理对象:textView.delegate = self

实现代理方法:

    func textView(textView: UITextView, shouldChangeTextInRange range: NSRange, replacementText text: String) -&gt; Bool {
    if text == &quot;\n&quot; {
        textView.resignFirstResponder()
        return false;
    }
    return true;
}
</code></pre>]]></content>
    
