    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>原作:<a href="http://ericasadun.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">Erica Sadun</a> 原文:<a href="http://ericasadun.com/2016/08/23/how-do-you-beautify-guard-else-conditions/" target="_blank" rel="external">地址</a></p>
</blockquote>
<p>这个看起来真的是可怕.</p>
<p><img src="http://ericasadun.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-23-at-11.03.47-AM.png" alt="code1"></p>
<p>这个看起来像错的:</p>
<p><img src="http://ericasadun.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-23-at-11.06.56-AM.png" alt="code2"></p>
<p>这个也是:</p>
<p><img src="http://ericasadun.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-23-at-11.07.50-AM.png" alt="code3"></p>
<p>还有这个:</p>
<p><img src="http://ericasadun.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-23-at-11.08.25-AM.png" alt="code4"></p>
<p>然后这两个都需要手工缩进:</p>
<p><img src="http://ericasadun.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-23-at-11.17.53-AM.png" alt="code5"></p>
<p><img src="http://ericasadun.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-23-at-11.17.59-AM.png" alt="code5"></p>
<p>这好像是其中最好的一个:</p>
<p><img src="http://ericasadun.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2016-08-23-at-11.08.59-AM.png" alt="code6"></p>
<p><strong>你准备怎样修复它呢?</strong></p>
<p><strong>Patrick Perini 建议这样:</strong><br><a href="https://gist.github.com/pcperini/3b556bfe9e183de617f829b9a48968fd#file-guard_beaut-swift" target="_blank" rel="external">guard_beaut.swift</a> hosted with ❤ by <a href="http://www.github.com" target="_blank" rel="external">GitHub</a></p>
<pre>
guard (
  !argument.isEmpty,
  nums.count == arguments.count
) else {
  print("Blah blah")
}
</pre>



<p><strong>Greg Titus 认为使用一个简单的语句和一个不会返回的函数会更好:</strong><br><a href="https://gist.github.com/erica/0819579b9a79f61ffa206154c9eb555c#file-viagreg-swift" target="_blank" rel="external">viagreg.swift</a> hosted with ❤ by <a href="http://www.github.com" target="_blank" rel="external">GitHub</a></p>
<pre>
// Usage
func usage() -> Never {
    print("Usage: \(appName) <list-of-positive-integers>")
    exit(-1)
}
guard !arguments.isEmpty,
    nums.count == arguments.count else { usage() }
</list-of-positive-integers></pre>

]]></content>
    
